 Lysyj-Krysztofiak, Warsaw 2016. We will recapture if needed with} 14... Nxc3 15. Bxc3 {and are also now all set to uncoil the potential in his position with 14...-- 15.Nxe4! dxe4 16.Ne5 .}) *

