so he should probably try to radically force the pace.}) 14. Qd4 $1 {Three black pieces now hang and there's only one decent move.} Nb3 15. Qxh8 Nxa1 16. Qxa1 Z0 ({Black doesn't have enough for the piece. White will surely be able to gradually untangle after Bd3 and Kf1 if needed, i.e., in the event of} 16... e6 17. Bd3 Bxb4+ 18. Kf1 {.}) *

