development, we can even allow the queens to come off. Black might decline, but then White can even consider Qc2, as well as ideas of h4-h5.} Qxb3 13. axb3 Z0 ({The half-open a-file in conjunction with White's ideas of Nb5 and Nd5 already makes life unpleasant for Black (} 13... c6 $4 14. Bxb6 {would not be wise), and the engines confirm that White has far too much compensation. Don't forget either just how awkward moves such as Bd4 and h4-h5 might be for Black to meet on the other wing.}) *

