1. Nf3 {Having just covered Black's most popular lines involving a kingside fianchetto, it makes sense to continue in that vein, although you'll have to wait until Chapter Seven for those ...f5 and ...g6 Leningrad Dutch style lines. Here our focus will be on:} Z0 ({6a:} 1... d6 {and}) (1... Nf6 2. c4 d6 {. 6b: The Modern, 1...g6 .}) *

