t White should just be doing fairly well.} 14. Qc2 {Clearly d5 is taboo and meanwhile White all set to take control with Rad1 and Bb2, as well as Nf4 if the knight is kicked. Factor in that Ne5 or Ng5 may follow and Black's defensive task does not seem such an appealing one.} *

