ng White's structure, although you may be happy to either seize space with} 7. d5 {or fight for the initiative with}) (7. dxc5 $5 {.}) 7... cxd4 8. Nxd4 Nc6 9. Be3 {We've reached an unusual type of Accelerated Dragon (Line 2B). Black is fairly active, but White does have the Maroczy Bind and should look to quickly house the king with Be2 and O-O.} *

